data.description: Remodeled CBS Pool Home in coveted South Fork Estates! 5-bed, 3-bath gem boasts a separate entrance 5th bedroom, perfect as a mother-in-law suite, oversized-office, or studio. Fully remodeled in 2021 with metal roof, new kitchen, flooring, appliances, light fixtures, plantation shutters, & fresh paint. Vaulted ceilings & open floorplan create a light-filled home. Solid CBS construction on almost 3/4 acre, offering spacious interiors, a screened pool/patio, overlooking the private backyard oasis. Stainless steel appliances, elegant master bath, dual sinks, spa tub, and separate shower. Community offers a playground & gated RV/boat parking (add'l fee as available). Enjoy low HOA fees, convenient shopping, and easy I-95 access. Public boat ramp for ocean access just minutes away! Call today! Sizes and Measurements are approximate. Buyer to verify all information.
